{"tid":1330859,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(戰術po)請各位比一分鐘時間我","createTime":"2019-07-18T17:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T11:29:16.000Z","uid":258411,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ccc06628b75722e84bb77e5e5c8b9914f59ba7fd","tid":1330859,"uid":258411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:22:18.000Z","msg":"Sorry我係P牌仔，但我想講好耐:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">使用護目鏡前請做防霧！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">使用護目鏡前請做防霧！</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">使用護目鏡前請做防霧！</span></span><br />\n依點好重要，但每次都唔見有巴打做，咁耐都無見巴打提起。<br />\n任何密封嘅護目鏡，<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rrAmiAB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrrAmiAB.png&h=46afdf2f&s={SIZE}\" />，包括3M鏡，泳鏡，full face gas mask都會起鏡面內側起霧，會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重阻礙視線</span></span>，而且你要除低副鏡先抹得到。你流得越多汗，護目鏡越密封，霧化越勁。<br />\n你大概唔會想起催淚氣體中間除眼罩或者盲左。<br />\n如果有巴打絲打一定要戴眼鏡，請起護目鏡內側，眼鏡內側以及外側共<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三層鏡面</span></span>做防霧處理。<br />\n方法有三<br />\n1.塗口水，個人認為最弱<br />\n2.洗潔精，用眼鏡布落啲洗潔精，抹一抹鏡面，少量即可<br />\n3.防霧噴劑或防霧塗劑，防霧塗劑使用比較容易，迪卡儂有售，39蚊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1KDGiEb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1KDGiEb.png&h=a39179db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三種方法都可以阻止水氣聚面於鏡面上。<br />\n仲有，防霧都唔係無敵，如非使用護目鏡當中，唔好將護目鏡戴起額頭等位置，可以時，盡量令護目鏡通風。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">都希望各位可以帶自己支防霧出黎，幫下啲唔知要防霧嘅巴打，依個真係好重要。得我一個幫唔到咁多位巴打做防霧</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6a3e80c695d47ec126f4dd3786200bd6f02f91","tid":1330859,"uid":258411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:23:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b2d86d86f173b56f3c3c4fca05baf9f8ae6b20f","tid":1330859,"uid":258411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"防霧記住查內側，查外側無用架！！"},{"pid":"9a6540c3016df7c5486a4851e46498a70eb18ac9","tid":1330859,"uid":258411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:38:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a516a382605e5d26a7faec8fdf1c466f13d69a88","tid":1330859,"uid":258411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:41:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45060ea12938285a6dd6a5d22ba3fea6ff4fa9c2","tid":1330859,"uid":258411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:41:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5955b433b00df44f39c3090c32dcc93320284fa","tid":1330859,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569ae0ed8f470989c85676d45fb05630bf923760","tid":1330859,"uid":98141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:45:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7cd93b24178de64bc6909183a6f1c616a93fdfd2","tid":1330859,"uid":264459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:38:52.000Z","msg":"防霧筆唔好搽泳鏡<br />\n試過唔知係咪副泳鏡本身已有塗層<br />\n搽完之後好似溶左啲膠咁濛哂<br />\n泳鏡即時睇唔到野報銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果真係有需要建議係角落位置試啲啲先"},{"pid":"fe72919964b5bc805ae24dd4931c1f1e718109f9","tid":1330859,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:40:00.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"b6c3333b48bb5d508bc728c1e4fc541cbd181797","tid":1330859,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:40:22.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"21d32f2b48ea190eedfa86b729605ba16578ad25","tid":1330859,"uid":258411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:27:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d5431af7ab8456d0add9b53a35b6e1d07ef8a4a","tid":1330859,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime